{"tid":2058771,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"記者被控暴動罪無人講？","createTime":"2020-06-10T12:09:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-12T12:32:36.000Z","uid":328383,"like":9,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"7d202344a17b2d86f00bad0b7015c7d0d3517061","tid":2058771,"uid":328383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:09:21.000Z","msg":"熱血時報的記者就不是記者嗎？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n七一入立法會採訪被加控暴動罪　本台記者馬啟聰准保釋8月再訊<br />\n<br />\n於去年7月1日採訪立法會實況的本台記者及主持人馬啟聰，原被控一項進入或逗留會議廳範圍，今午（6月10日）在東區裁判法院再訊時，被加控一項暴動罪。  <br />\n<br />\n控方加控一項修訂控罪，指馬啟聰與其他人參與暴動。本案共12名被告暫時毋須答辯，控方申請轉去區域法院，案件押後至8月3日再訊，以待所需文件，各被告准以原有條件保釋。  同案其他被告，包括藝人王宗堯、港大學生會前會長孫曉嵐、民間團隊發言人劉頴匡都同被加控暴動罪。  <br />\n<br />\n去年7月1日示威者攻佔立法會當晚，持有本台記者證的馬啟聰，於立法會內採訪及直播。 <br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-10-2020/63466\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F06-10-2020%2F63466&d=TNVh%2FXBsTmD9bRjMILuVa1SbKypX9O9wpAPGBeI%2BXHg%3D&h=e3c800d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/06-10-2020/63466</a>"},{"pid":"c5c65010e3e3068fd02f77bcd6fb7f4ac83bd1d8","tid":2058771,"uid":31521,"like":6,"dislike":35,"score":-29,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:12:18.000Z","msg":"熱狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502c58d8d4a2e372df1206e4025fddc3f14fabee","tid":2058771,"uid":44171,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"反蝗年代佢有個手足重判佢地自己都無理過，咁上下啦, 個果應該都未放監<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6694228c6ddee25d54c88c8542dfa17605503db","tid":2058771,"uid":8500,"like":11,"dislike":2,"scor